    </sentence>
    <sentence id="DDI-DrugBank.d511.s2" text="one patient died with severe hypocalcemia."/>
    <sentence id="DDI-DrugBank.d511.s3" text="Toxicity associated with concomitant use of aerosolized pentamidine has not been reported.">
